snippet.title: Kindling: The Last Light Gameplay
snippet.description:
They smothered the sun and choked the light from our world. One light remains.

Challenge yourself to play both characters, or play local co-op with a friend to be stronger together.

Play at: https://cookiecrayon.itch.io/kindling
